{"tid":2387953,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【 ﻿走資去台灣﻿ (一) 】ATM 螞蟻搬家","createTime":"2021-01-30T17:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T18:10:35.000Z","uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"958fc3fce034ff9548695b74c766b5d782473c83","tid":2387953,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"【分享 #銀聯咭 港幣換台幣心得】<br />\n<br />\n人在台灣，如果想從香港/澳門戶口提取新台幣，作一般生活開銷，可以同旅行時一樣，去 ATM 撳錢，單次最高新台幣 20,000。<br />\n⠀<br />\n保守啲計，單日撳2次新台幣 20,000 (總共新台幣 40,000)，係冇問題嘅，至於單日上限係幾多，就要睇返發咭銀行規定，以及個人「海外自動櫃員機提款限額」設定。<br />\n⠀<br />\n我自己係用銀聯提款卡，到有銀聯 logo 嘅 ATM 提款，一般超市 (全聯、小北)、便利店 (711、全家) 都有。<br />\n⠀<br />\n除咗方便，匯率一路無得輸，而且銀行只收有限手續費 (e.g.恆生/匯豐每次HK$20，中銀/星展每次 HK$15)。<br />\n⠀<br />\n注意：係「銀聯提款卡」，非「銀聯信用卡」。<br />\n用「銀聯信用卡」提取現金，會另收 1%-1.2% 手續費。<br />\n⠀<br />\n順帶一提，試過有次趕時間，用香港花旗提款咭 (非銀聯) 撳新台幣，個 rate 冇咁靚都算，手續費仲要&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nRead more:<br />\nMeWe: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3pAvfSO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3pAvfSO&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=b75f7d63\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3pAvfSO</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3r5JRdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3r5JRdf&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=01ded379\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3r5JRdf</a>"},{"pid":"c6934606b994acfadefbcf3ac58522cbaea39a22","tid":2387953,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"你人在台灣，開HSBC TW 再由HSBC HK 轉錢過去咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ff467dda6ed5c72612b4036213c27c83768e25","tid":2387953,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"2樓秒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63856db927e2ecc00295c8e8530eae1dce944304","tid":2387953,"uid":3328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6934606b994acf